Sean Harris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sean_Harris 0 Sean Harris is an English actor and writer. He is known for his role as Solomon Lane in the films Mission: Impossible – Rogue Nation (2015) and Mission: Impossible – Fallout (2018). Harris won a British Academy Television Award for Best Actor for his role in the miniseries Southcliffe (2013). He also received three consecutive BIFA Award for Best Supporting Actor nominations.
